<plot>In the first of the third (1941-42 season) RKO series of shorts based on the popular radio program, Information Please, noted foreign correspondent John Gunther joins regular panel member Oscar Levant, Franklyn P. Adams and moderator Clifton Fadiman. The quiz ends with song title pantomimes, with the experts missing on "Three Little Words."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?264916</url></doc>
